author: Khaleej Times
title: UAE at 2015 China Arab States Expo
text: (MENAFN - Khaleej Times)The UAE represented by the Ministry of Economy is to participate in the 2015 China-Arab States Expo to be held from September 10-13 in the International Trade Center of Chinese Muslims in the north-western Chinese city of Yinchuan Ningxia Province. The exhibition is a major international platform with its constant evolution communication and consultations between the two sides which has intensified the economic and trade fields.
